# DEPLOYING 2048-game IN AWS USING EKS

- created ec2 instance and added iam role with permissions-Ec2fullaccess,AWScloudformationFullaccess,AWSIamFullaccess,Administrator access.
  
![image](https://github.com/devulapallideepika/2048-game/assets/129947829/3b779e76-c603-4fde-a4b0-5e1f4b7b775e)

- In ec2 instance installed awscli,kubectl,eksctl .
  
![image](https://github.com/devulapallideepika/2048-game/assets/129947829/ae524bfa-a7fb-4f3a-8d26-7825da14abf7)
![image](https://github.com/devulapallideepika/2048-game/assets/129947829/c71d13b3-83ca-4f11-a0ec-4c34b716e3bb)
![image](https://github.com/devulapallideepika/2048-game/assets/129947829/429891ba-2aac-423f-a733-e17b709cfb90)

- creating eksctl cluster
  
![image](https://github.com/devulapallideepika/2048-game/assets/129947829/76e3a798-5574-46c7-9a8b-d9ad4c171e29)

- created deployment.yml file.
  
![image](https://github.com/devulapallideepika/2048-game/assets/129947829/23719fcc-d8e8-4f00-9ed9-488ed40cbcac)

- created service.yml file.
  
![image](https://github.com/devulapallideepika/2048-game/assets/129947829/c0497c7c-d770-4607-b2ca-c447ee1a0b0c)

- kubectl apply -f filename - command creates the pod, service.
  
![image](https://github.com/devulapallideepika/2048-game/assets/129947829/cc881ce5-960f-45eb-b9f8-4921de7dcd23) 

- deployment,service created.
  
- ACCESS THE APPLICATION USING LOADBALANCER
  
![image](https://github.com/devulapallideepika/2048-game/assets/129947829/b4828272-225b-486e-824e-7d07b8b71a0c)
   
